         |1=[[鉤鼻龍屬|著名鉤鼻龍]] ''Gryposaurus notabilis''
         |2=[[鉤鼻龍屬|紀念區鉤鼻龍]] ''Gryposaurus monumentensis'' }} }} }} }} }} }} }} }} }} }}

==古生物學==
===病理===
2003年在一個短冠龍化石發現了{{link-en|血管瘤|hemangiomas}}、{{link-en|成纖維性纖維瘤|desmoplastic fibroma}}、[[遠端轉移|轉移癌]]、{{link-en|成骨細胞瘤|Osteoblastoma}}等[[腫瘤|腫瘤]]跡象。羅斯柴爾德等人使用[[電腦斷層掃描|電腦斷層掃描]]與{{link-en|螢光鏡|Fluoroscopy}}成影，檢驗多種恐龍的脊椎。數種其他鴨嘴龍類，包含[[埃德蒙頓龍|埃德蒙頓龍]]、[[計氏龍|計氏龍]]、[[巴克龍|巴克龍]]的檢驗結果也呈陽性。在超過一萬個化石中，腫瘤只在短冠龍與其近親有發現。腫瘤的成因可能是環境因素或遺傳規律。<ref name="Rothschildetal">{{cite journal| last = Rothschild| first = B.M.|author2=Tanke, D.H. |author3=Helbling II, M. |author4=Martin, L.D.| title = Epidemiologic study of tumors in dinosaurs| journal = Naturwissenschaften| volume = 90| issue = 11| pages = 495–500| year = 2003| doi = 10.1007/s00114-003-0473-9| pmid = 14610645}}</ref>

===食性===
一份2008年的研究對木乃伊標本「李奧納多」進行檢驗，發現其吃的食物包含[[樹葉|樹葉]]、[[毬果|毬果]]、[[蕨類|蕨類]]、[[開花植物|開花植物]]（如[[木蘭屬|木蘭屬]]）。研究亦發現短冠龍具有多方位的[[植食性|植食性]]習性，同時是{{link-en|覽植者|Browsing (herbivory)}}也是{{link-en|刮植者|Grazing (behaviour)}}，但根據胃中發現的內容物，似乎比較偏向前者。<ref name=JTetal2008>{{cite journal |last=Tweet |first=Tweet, Justin S. |author2=Chin, Karen |author3=Braman, Dennis R. |author4= Murphy, Nate L.  |year=2008 |title=Probable gut contents within a specimen of ''Brachylophosaurus canadensis'' (Dinosauria: Hadrosauridae) from the Upper Cretaceous Judith River Formation of Montana |journal=PALAIOS |volume=23 |issue=9/10 |pages=624–635 |doi=10.2110/palo.2007.p07-044r}}</ref><ref name="RobinLloyd">{{Cite news |last=Lloyd |first=Robin |work=NBC News |title=Plant-eating dinosaur spills his guts: Fossil suggests hadrosaur's last meal included lots of well-chewed leaves |date=2008-09-25 |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/26893497 |access-date=2009-07-03 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806131605/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/26893497 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Walley |first1=Mike |title=Contents of a Dinosaur’s Stomach – Eats, Shoots and Leaves (apologies to Lynne Truss) |url=https://blog.everythingdinosaur.co.uk/blog/_archives/2008/09/25/3900640.html |website=Everything Dinosaur: Discover Everything |access-date=25 September 2008 |archive-date=2021-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210819163530/https://blog.everythingdinosaur.co.uk/blog/_archives/2008/09/25/3900640.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Hecht |first1=Jeff |title=Perfectly preserved dinosaur stuns palaeontologists |url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg17623650-500-perfectly-preserved-dinosaur-stuns-palaeontologists/ |website=NewScientist |publisher=New Scientist Ltd. |access-date=19 October 2002 |archive-date=2021-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210819163538/https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg17623650-500-perfectly-preserved-dinosaur-stuns-palaeontologists/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Stokstad |first1=Erik |title=Dinosaur 'Mummy' Unveiled |url=https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2002/10/dinosaur-mummy-unveiled |website=Science Magazine |publisher=merican Association for the Advancement of Science |access-date=18 October 2002 |archive-date=2021-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210819183852/https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2002/10/dinosaur-mummy-unveiled |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Mayell |first1=Hillary |title="Mummified" Dinosaur Discovered In Montana |url=https://www.biologyonline.com/articles/quotmummifiedquot-dinosaur-discovered-montana |website=Biology Online |publisher=Biology Online |access-date=18 July 2006 |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228064335/https://www.biologyonline.com/articles/quotmummifiedquot-dinosaur-discovered-montana |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Rare, Mummified Dinosaur Moves into New Home at The Children's Museum of Indianapolis |url=https://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/03/prweb11658575.htm |website=CISION PRWeb |publisher=PRWeb |access-date=12 March 2014 |archive-date=2021-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210819163533/https://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/03/prweb11658575.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==古生態學==
[[恐龍公園層|恐龍公園層]]與[[恐龍省立公園|恐龍省立公園]]中某些較少見鴨嘴龍科化石，例如短冠龍，可能是遷徙經過該地區時死亡的。牠們可能原本生活在較偏高原的棲息地，在那裏進行築巢、覓食等行為。<ref name="tanke-brett-surman-2001">Tanke, D.H. and Brett-Surman, M.K. 2001. Evidence of Hatchling and Nestling-Size Hadrosaurs (Reptilia:Ornithischia) from Dinosaur Provincial Park (Dinosaur Park Formation: Campanian), Alberta, Canada. pp. 206-218. In: Mesozoic Vertebrate Life—New Research Inspired by the Paleontology of Philip J. Currie. Edited by D.H. Tanke and K. Carpenter. Indiana University Press: Bloomington. xviii + 577 pp.</ref>

